{"type":"message","id":"f1561b75","parentId":"0dbdda0e","timestamp":"2026-03-03T09:46:24.083Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我还是遇到了需要 target 参数的问题。看起来没有 target 参数无法直接在这里发送消息。我应该直接回复用户而不使用 message 工具。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉命令格式错误。请你运行：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw help config\n```\n\n查看 config 命令的正确用法。\n\n或者我们换个思路 — 能否直接检查当前的权限配置？运行：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw status\n```\n\n这会显示当前会话的配置信息，包括可用工具和权限。\n\n把输出结果发给我，我会根据实际情况调整方案。\n\n或者，如果这个 webchat 界面没有文件操作权限，你可以告诉我：\n- 你的 OpenClaw 是如何在其他界面运行的（如 Discord、Terminal）？\n- 那里是否启用了完整的工具权限？\n\n我可以在有完整权限的会话中继续实施这个工作流系统。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen3","model":"GLM-4.7-FP8","usage":{"input":23060,"output":173,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23233,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772531176491}}
{"type":"message","id":"c807f0cb","parentId":"f1561b75","timestamp":"2026-03-03T09:46:59.030Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-03 17:46 GMT+8] (base) ➜ openclawCode openclaw status\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.2 (85377a2) — Your config is valid, your assumptions are not.\n\n│\n◇\n│\n◇\nOpenClaw status\n\nOverview\n┌─────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Item │ Value │\n├─────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Dashboard │ http://127.0.0.1:18789/ │\n│ OS │ macos 14.5 (arm64) · node 25.7.0 │\n│ Tailscale │ off │\n│ Channel │ stable (default) │\n│ Update │ pnpm · npm latest 2026.3.2 │\n│ Gateway │ local · ws://127.0.0.1:18789 (local loopback) · reachable 41ms · auth token · lihzz.local (10.192.82.11) app │\n│ │ 2026.3.2 macos 14.5 │\n│ Gateway service │ LaunchAgent installed · loaded · running (pid 52719) │\n│ Node service │ LaunchAgent not installed │\n│ Agents │ 1 · 1 bootstrap file present · sessions 1 · default main active just now │\n│ Memory │ 0 files · 0 chunks · dirty · sources memory · plugin memory-core · vector unknown · fts ready · cache on (0) │\n│ Probes │ skipped (use --deep) │\n│ Events │ none │\n│ Heartbeat │ 30m (main) │\n│ Sessions │ 1 active · default GLM-4.7-FP8 (262k ctx) · ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/sessions.json │\n└─────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\nSecurity audit\nSummary: 1 critical · 2 warn · 1 info\n CRITICAL State dir is world-writable\n /Users/lihzz/.openclaw mode=777; other users can write into your OpenClaw state.\n Fix: chmod 700 /Users/lihzz/.openclaw\n WARN Reverse proxy headers are not trusted\n gateway.bind is loopback and gateway.trustedProxies is empty. If you expose the Control UI through a reverse proxy, configure trusted proxies so local-client c…\n Fix: Set gateway.trustedProxies to your proxy IPs or keep the Control UI local-only.\n WARN Some gateway.nodes.denyCommands entries are ineffective\n gateway.nodes.denyCommands uses exact node command-name matching only (for example `system.run`), not shell-text filtering inside a command payload. - Unknown …\n Fix: Use exact command names (for example: canvas.present, canvas.hide, canvas.navigate, canvas.eval, canvas.snapshot, canvas.a2ui.push, canvas.a2ui.pushJSONL, canvas.a2ui.reset). If you need broader restrictions, remove risky command IDs from allowCommands/default workflows and tighten tools.exec policy.\nFull report: openclaw security audit\nDeep probe: openclaw security audit --deep\n\nChannels\n┌──────────┬─────────┬────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Channel │ Enabled │ State │ Detail │\n├──────────┼─────────┼────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n└──────────┴─────────┴────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\nSessions\n┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┬────────┬──────────┬──────────────┬────────────────┐\n│ Key │ Kind │ Age │ Model │ Tokens │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────┼──────────┼──────────────┼────────────────┤\n│ agent:main:main │ direct │ just now │ GLM-4.7-FP8 │ 23k/262k (9%) │\n└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┴────────┴──────────┴──────────────┴────────────────┘\n\nFAQ: https://docs.openclaw.ai/faq\nTroubleshooting: https://docs.openclaw.ai/troubleshooting\n\nNext steps:\n Need to share? openclaw status --all\n Need to debug live? openclaw logs --follow\n Need to test channels? openclaw status --deep"}],"timestamp":1772531219016}}
{"type":"message","id":"1f4a7c12","parentId":"c807f0cb","timestamp":"2026-03-03T09:47:17.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我看到了 openclaw status 的输出。我注意到：\n\n1. Gateway 是本地运行的，通过 ws://127.0.0.1:18789\n2. 有一个安全警告：State dir 是 world-writable（mode=777）\n3. Dashboard 在 http://127.0.0.1:18789/\n4. Current session 使用 GLM-4.7-FP8 模型\n\n但是这个输出并没有显示工具权限信息。用户现在在终端中，可以运行命令。\n\n让我建议用户检查配置文件或者直接让我提供完整的脚本和配置文件内容，让用户手动创建。\n\n不过，用户说\"Claude Code 我已经本地部署了一个Claude Code 你直接启动他跟他对话就行\"，这意味着我需要能够启动 Claude Code。\n\n当前的问题是我没有 bash 工具可用。让我看看是否可以通过其他方式：\n\n1. 我可以提供完整的脚本和配置文件内容\n2. 用户手动创建文件\n3. 用户运行我提供的命令\n\n或者，我应该问用户：\n- 是否可以通过其他界面（如 Discord、SSH terminal）运行，那里可能有完整的工具权限\n- 还是我们就采用手动创建文件的方式\n\n让我提供一个折中方案：我先为用户准备好所有的脚本和配置文件内容，用户创建后可以手动运行初始化脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看到你的 OpenClaw 状态了。当前这个 webchat 会话没有显示工具权限信息。\n\n## 方案：手动创建系统\n\n既然当前会话权限有限，我为你准备完整的工作流系统。请按以下步骤操作：\n\n### 第 1 步：创建项目基础结构\n\n进入项目目录并创建目录：\n\n```bash\ncd /Users/lihzz/openclawCode\n\n# 创建目录结构\nmkdir -p agents/tasks\nmkdir -p agents/agents\nmkdir -p agents/scripts\nmkdir -p agents/logs\nmkdir -p agents/config\nmkdir -p meeting-records\nmkdir -p reviews\n```\n\n### 第 2 步：将准备好所有脚本文件\n\n我会为你准备好以下文件：\n\n1. **requirements.txt** - Python 依赖\n2. **start_agent.sh** - 启动 Claude Code agent\n3. **setup_worktree.sh** - 创建 git worktree\n4. **monitor_agents.py** - 监控脚本\n5. **cli.py** - 主 CLI 接口\n6. **pr_reviewer.py** - 自动 PR reviewer\n7. **email_notifier.py** - 邮件通知器\n8. **task_tracker.json** - 任务跟踪配置\n\n你想让我现在就开始提供这些文件的内容吗？我会一个一个给你，你按照我提供的文件名和路径保存即可。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen3","model":"GLM-4.7-FP8","usage":{"input":24182,"output":554,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24736,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772531219017}}
